<br>
Which means, the hardest hitters will show more dmg, as you can't see the dmg effects of a water pet.<br>
<br>
It really can be a fun spell though. I went to a guild wedding two nights ago, the wedding was in the EC tunnel, and i managed to conjure up a cute yellow spider. Too bad we couldn't quite animate him enough to be the ring bearer..... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
